-- Bharti Airtel Names Devender Singh Rawat Chief Executive of Infratel Unit
-- Madelene Pearson
-- 2010-08-01T07:59:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-01/bharti-airtel-names-devender-singh-rawat-chief-executive-of-infratel-unit.html

          
          
             Bharti Airtel Ltd. named Devender
Singh Rawat as chief executive officer at its Bharti Infratel
Ltd. unit, the company in an e-mailed statement today.   
